# React (NXTCM-components)

- Prefer functional components over class-based ones
- Implement proper dependency arrays in useEffect/useCallback/useMemo
- Use custom hooks for business logic separation
- Prefer React Form Wizard onValueChange over useEffect for reacting to form value changes
- Use useMemo for expensive computations that would otherwise re-run on every render
- Prefer useCallback when passing callbacks to memoized child components or when a stable reference is needed to avoid unnecessary re-renders
- Use proper key props for list items
